(1, 16, '9', '6 Rich Experiences to Try on Saudi\'s Coasts', 'Looking for some adventure in the Middle East? How about a trip to the unexplored coasts of Saudi Arabia? From swimming with exotic fishes, sailing through lush mangroves, to relaxing on pristine, golden beaches, you are bound to find something that will attract you to the Saudi coasts. Let\'s have a look at 6 experiences that will bring you back to Saudi again and again.', '<p><strong>1. Scuba Diving Along the Red Sea</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/scuba_2.jpg\" alt=\"scuba\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Sea activities like scuba diving can make any holiday memorable! In Saudi Arabia, scuba diving in the Red Sea allows you to swim amongst nearly 1,200 species of fish, almost 20 per cent of which are unique to the area. Explore the coral reefs and discover the ruins and treasures of shipwrecks from throughout history.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Explore the Farasan Islands</strong></p>\r\n<p>Some parts of the world are home to stunning natural ecosystems. Explore the rich history and marine life while sailing through the azure waters and mangroves of the Farasan Islands. Check out manta rays, whale sharks, dolphins and sea turtles in the bays and inlets of the island. Step ashore and lose yourself in the depths of the Al-Qandal forest, visit Al-Qassar village and the islands\' past as a Roman garrison, the furthest outpost of the empire.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Kiteboard in Jeddah</strong></p>\r\n<p>Take advantage of soft, sandy beaches, clear, shallow waters, and consistent year-round winds when kiteboarding off the coast of Jeddah. Feel the cool, temperate, yet sunny winters that coincide with ideal wind speeds to create the perfect winter getaway for water-sports enthusiasts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. Relax on the Beaches of Umluj</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/umluj_1.jpg\" alt=\"umluj\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Are you a beach person? The secluded beaches of Umluj, in the northern province of Tabuk, provide the ideal opportunity to escape and immerse yourself in unspoiled nature. The pristine waters allow you to observe marine life without the need for a mask and snorkel. Enjoy a picnic on the beach or rent a boat from the village\'s port to explore the untouched islands a short sail from the coast.</p>\r\n<p><strong>5. Sample the Day&rsquo;s Catch At Jeddah&rsquo;s Seafood Market</strong></p>\r\n<p>For a taste of the sea, make your way to Jeddah\'s port and watch the local fisherman offload their hauls at sunrise before jostling with other buyers to bid on the freshest catch at Central Fish Market. Tuck into an unrivalled variety of seafood that has been prepared, cooked and served mere hours after being caught while learning of the port\'s fascinating role in Jeddah\'s history as a global trading hub and entry point for pilgrims travelling onto the two holy cities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>6. Enjoy an Eco-Friendly Holiday at the Red Sea Project</strong></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/project.jpg\" alt=\"project\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></p>\r\n<p>Unwind at Saudi Arabia\'s latest coastal retreat that caters to the environmentally conscious traveller. This luxury tourism development project spans an archipelago of 90 islands along the shores of the Tabuk province on the west coast of the Kingdom. The resort - set to open its first rooms in 2022 - is being developed with the protection of the Red Sea\'s ecosystem in mind. It will aim to be powered by 100% renewable energy, eventually generating and storing energy used onsite from renewable sources. Single-use plastics will be completely banned as carbon-neutral, yet the luxurious experience will signal a sustainable future for holidaying. So, it\'s a win-win situation for nature as well as the tourists!</p>\r\n<p>If the sea is where your heart is then Saudi Arabia can be your perfect pick for your next trip. If not all, try at least a few of these Red Sea experiences for a refreshing break in the Middle East!</p>', ' ', '1649799058-scuba_2.jpg', '1649799058-scuba_21.jpg', '6-rich-experiences-to-try-on-saudi-s-coasts', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:00:58', 15),
(2, 16, '9', 'A Road Trip to the Heart of India: Madhya Pradesh', 'Four families travelling in four cars for 4000 kilometres for 14 days. An impossible journey, some might say. But here we were, taking a road trip to magical Madhya Pradesh or the ‘Heart of India’.', '<p><strong>Madhya Pradesh - The Heart of India</strong></p>\r\n<p>Madhya Pradesh (MP) happens to be one of my home states. It has plenty of things to offer &ndash; forts and palaces (Maheshwar, Gwalior &amp; Orchha), jungles ((Panna, Ken, Kanha, Satpuda &amp; Bhimbetka), temples (Khajuraho, Datia &amp; Maihar), hills (Pachmarhi), rivers (Narmada &amp; Ken) and lakes (Bhopal). And this was just where we travelled! However, there is much more to Madhya Pradesh than this.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In Madhya Pradesh, there is always something interesting to see every 200-400 kilometres: and it is best to explore the region in your own vehicle. Driving allows you the freedom of time and movement (something that a train may not be able to do). Moreover, the airports are not always close to your intended destination, so you will end up hiring a car. So, it is better to opt for a road trip. Most roads in the state are in good condition. Some sections are exceptionally well developed &ndash; the national and state highways that you will use are mostly well made. However, there are sections where work is going on to make them wider or better. This leads to diversions currently, which can make driving somewhat tedious. Hopefully, once the new roads are built, driving around will become easier.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So, now that you know the best way to explore Madhya Pradesh, let&rsquo;s check out the itinerary!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Where to Go</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/970x587-blog-Itinerary.jpg\" alt=\"itinerary\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>In the next sections, we will let photos tell the story.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Maheshwar:</em></strong>&nbsp;The Shiv Panchayat, the&nbsp;<em>tani-bani</em>&nbsp;sarees, the history of the fort and Ahalya Bai make this an interesting short detour on the way to Indore from Mumbai. Both Wikipedia and local guides say that this place was earlier called Mahishmati (so all you fans of Bahubali&mdash;go see where the history actually began).</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/970x587-blog-Maheshwar.jpg\" alt=\"maheshwar\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Indore:</em></strong>&nbsp;We missed exploring the historical landmarks as we had camped in the city for both legs of our trip as the anchor destination. We had long drives coming into Indore both times. So all that we explored were the eateries at Chappan Dukan. The city and some of its surrounding areas have a lot more to offer. Since we can always come back here more easily, in a long MP trip, Indore remained underexplored.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Bhopal:</em></strong>&nbsp;The City of Lakes has a fantastic evening experience to offer in its speedboats (which is what we took) and cruises. Keep traffic in mind while reaching the boarding point, but once you are in the speedboat and can see the sun setting in the waters of the lake, the experience will be worth the effort. If you have time (we left Indore late, but you could reach Bhopal earlier in the day), definitely visit the tribal museum&mdash;<em>Manav Sanghrahalaya</em>.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/970x587-blog-boatinginbhopal.jpg\" alt=\"bhopal\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Sanchi:&nbsp;</em></strong>This was the first of the three UNESCO World Heritage sites in MP that we explored. Find a good guide and you can happily spend hours learning about the history of the Ashokan era. For us, time just flew! One popular photo location is the angle from where the imprint on the new Rs. 200 note has been taken. If you are there, don&rsquo;t miss the location.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/970x587-blog-sanchistupa.jpg\" alt=\"sanchi\" width=\"970\" height=\"587\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Bhimbetka:</em></strong>&nbsp;We came to the second world heritage site in a day! Again, a good guide can help you get up-to-date with some fascinating history of humanity, going back tens of thousands of years and some very beautiful scenes to shoot. Remember you will be walking a lot at both Sanchi and Bhimbetka. Plan for that too.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You can&rsquo;t plan for a trip to Madhya Pradesh and not talk about its food! Indore is famous worldwide for its spicy, delicious, lip-smacking dishes. There is no better way to experience it all than at Chappan Dukan and its stalls. Especially on a wintry night, the hot&nbsp;<em>garadus</em>,&nbsp;<em>bhutte ka kees</em>&nbsp;and the cheesy potato spirals are a delight. Top that up with&nbsp;<em>thandai</em>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<em>paan&nbsp;</em>and you will be in your own foodie heaven.</p>\r\n<p>At Gwalior, Taj Usha Kiran is the place to visit and stay. If you love spicy food, try the Nepalese-Marathi cuisine there and the vegetable dish with 18 spices! You will be amazed to find fantastic continental, tribal, Indian, and global cuisines in the middle of the Kanha jungle at the Pugdundee Resort. They can arrange for such a fabulous outdoor dining arrangement. At Panchmarhi, you can enjoy a chilly night with melodious and lively live music. The food experience at the WelcomHeritage Golf View in Panchmarhi is simply divine.</p>\r\n<p>Lest you think you need to be budget-conscious or stay at top-end hotels to get good food, you will be mistaken. All the eateries that we stopped at had hot, authentic Indian food for all ages and palates&ndash;&nbsp;<em>dhabas</em>&nbsp;at Maihar and Katni, the food court at Dodi (between Bhopal and Indore), and the Badri Seth Marwadi Bhoj and Raja Caf&eacute; at Khajurao.</p>\r\n<p>The one thing you can relax about on your trip to MP is the food. The heart of the country takes its taste palate very seriously!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Some Driving Tips</strong></p>\r\n<p>Google Maps works in almost all places. However, it is best to call ahead and ask which route to take. For example, on the way to Pachmarhi), there were two routes &ndash; one ended up being a dead-end. Similarly, the routes in and out of Kanha required some help from the local resort. Otherwise, maps work fine in the cities.</p>\r\n<p>We had a couple of instances with the potholes too. A pothole just before the last toll while entering Gwalior caused a rear tyre of a car to burst (not just puncture), and at Seoni (on the drive from Kanha to Pachmarhi), a pothole caused a car to slam the brakes suddenly, leading to an accident with the car behind. In both cases, there were no injuries or damage to any luggage. However, the cars took some beating. Thankfully, locals were cooperative and the car helplines worked. The experience can be traumatic, especially if it happens late at night.</p>\r\n<p>In many places, the parking capacity cannot handle the tourist rush. Maihar and Dhuadhaar Falls are two key examples. In Kanha and Pachmarhi, you will end up driving in the local Gypsy car most of the time (though in Pachmarhi, you can access many sightseeing points without needing a Gypsy car).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This one is not so much a driving tip as a routing one. We could have chosen to travel to Jhansi instead of Gwalior (or along with Gwalior). If we had a couple of days more, we could have planned a stop at Amarkantak &ndash; the origin point of Narmada. We missed Mandu, Omkareshwar, Udaygiri and other more famous spots in MP. Depending on your interest, you can plan to include some of these places in your itinerary.</p>\r\n<p>The best part of the driving for us was that we had four cars and had four families with us. This meant we could spend a lot of time with each other at every location. In this day and age of WhatsApp calls, it is not a road trip if the passengers don&rsquo;t dial in each other in a group call and play a<em>ntakshari</em>!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hurrah, Madhya Pradesh!</strong></p>\r\n<p>MP has typically been one of the most underrated places when it comes to local Indian tourism. I hope you take this road &ndash; it is a charming one, which will offer you a wide variety of choices and memories of a lifetime!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' ', '1649799246-mp.jpg', '1649799246-mp1.jpg', 'a-road-trip-to-the-heart-of-india-madhya-pradesh', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:04:06', 15),
(3, 16, '9', '8 Mind-blowing Experiences Cannot Miss on to Abu Dhabi!', 'The glittering capital of the United Arab Emirates, Abu Dhabi is a modern metropolis filled with gleaming buildings, fantastic architecture, coastal wonders and enough history to keep all kinds of travellers happy. The cultural heart of the UAE, Abu Dhabi has an old-world charm that will leave you mesmerised! From historical treasures, cruising in a traditional dhow boat to sandboarding and dune bashing in the endless dunes of desert, Abu Dhabi has it all!', '&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Catch a Glimpse of the Past at Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;lazy&quot; src=&quot;https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/sight-seeing.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;mosque&quot; width=&quot;970&quot; height=&quot;587&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque was completed in 2007 and can fit 40,000 visitors and worshippers. On your visit to the mosque, check out the pure white architecture which is a perfect portrayal of cross-cultural influences. With tall arches, reflective pools, marble domes and stunning chandeliers, a visit to the mosque makes for a transcendental experience! Non-Muslim visitors are allowed into all areas of the mosque (including the vast library). Every part of the mosque will narrate a story of the past and you can get a better understanding of the UAE&amp;rsquo;s history in their vast library.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Visit Saadiyat Island&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;lazy&quot; src=&quot;https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/saadiyatjpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;970&quot; height=&quot;587&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Peppered with white sand beaches and clear blue water, Saadiyat Island is your hub for some downtime from the city! Here, travellers can experience wonderful beach resorts along with delectable dining, spas, and a plethora of activities and excursions. While you are visiting Saadiyat Island, don&amp;rsquo;t miss out on a tour of the grand Louvre Abu Dhabi museum! Travellers can indulge in other actives like book tee time on the spectacular 18-hole championship golf course or head out for a paddle around the mangroves&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Visit the Mangrove National Park&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Home to notable natural wonders, the Mangrove National Park offers delightful experiences for nature and adventure enthusiasts! With over 60 species of birds in residence at the park, it&amp;rsquo;s a wonderful spot for bird watching. There are also scenic waterways that are perfect for kayaking. The stunning mangroves are a sight &amp;ndash; sitting 15-feet tall, with their long root system that seems to &amp;lsquo;snorkel&amp;rsquo; out of the saltwater for air. To get a closer look, you can sign up for one of the night tours and explore the mangroves by gliding through the waters after dark.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Roll with a Desert Safari&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;lazy&quot; src=&quot;https://seoimgak.mmtcdn.com/blog/sites/default/files/images/desert-dune.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;desert&quot; width=&quot;970&quot; height=&quot;587&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;One of the most popular attractions of Abu Dhabi is hands down the stunning Desert Safari! On a trip to the desert, explore the lovely Liwa Oasis, which lies at the edge of the Empty Quarter. The Empty Quarter desert is home to some of the largest sand dunes in the world and makes for a great playground to try snowboarding, camel trekking and dune buggy activities. An unforgettable experience here is the evening desert safari where travellers can go on a 4x4 dune escape and then watch a traditional tanura belly dance show and cap the night with stargazing!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Discover the Historical Treasures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;The walled compound in the west part of Abu Dhabi is home to a collection of magnificent governmental buildings. Visitors can take guided tours that afford highlights of Arabic literature in the Qasr Al Watan Library, the mosaics of The Great Hall, the artefacts and scrolls in the House of Knowledge and the stunning Presidential Palace - Qasr Al Watan.&amp;nbsp; Visitors can taste the royal lifestyle, by checking in at the neighbouring Emirates Palace, a lavish hotel that is set within acres of landscaped gardens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Meet Falcons at the Abu Dhabi Falcon Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;The Abu Dhabi Falcon Hospital is a veterinary hospital for ill and injured falcons, but here visitors can take guided tours that&amp;rsquo;ll allow them to get close to the falcons in the wards. There is also an on-site museum that explains the history of falconry. The tours must be pre-booked in advance. Travellers may also have the chance to hold one of the birds or even feed one. However, keep in mind, this activity is not for the faint-hearted!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. High Tea at the Observation Deck&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;The Observation Deck at 300 is the highest vantage point in Abu Dhabi. Located on the 74th floor of the Conrad Abu Dhabi Etihad Towers hotel, which soars 300 meters above sea level, the views of the city skyline, Corniche and Arabian Gulf from the deck will leave you enthralled! There is an entry fee for non-guests of the hotel, but the tickets can be redeemed for food and drinks at the Observation Deck&amp;rsquo;s restaurant. Soak up the popular high-tea experience around dusk and admire the stellar skyline!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Sunset Cruise in a Dhow Boat&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Traditional wooden dhows offer a glimpse of the times gone by when Abu Dhabi was the centre of the pearl diving industry! Today, travellers can live the old ways by tasting succulent dates and aromatic Arabic coffee while the sun turns the horizon to gold. Later, travellers can go below the deck for dinner and then post-dessert, relax and gaze up at the stellar night sky to wrap up their evenings in a magical manner!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;So while there is a lot to explore in this exciting city, we hope you club these experiences on your sojourn to explore Abu Dhabi.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '1649799343-dubai.jpg', '1649799343-dubai1.jpg', '8-mind-blowing-experiences-cannot-miss-on-to-abu-dhabi', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 23:59:22', 15),
(4, 25, '19, 17, 12', 'Unpaid Medical Debt Loses More of Its Financial Stigma', 'In the latest effort to remove the punitive effects of having overdue medical debt on credit records, the White House is directing federal agencies that make loans to ignore a track record of unpaid medical bills whenever possible.', '<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-4\" class=\"comp text-passage mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\">President Joe Biden on Monday ordered agencies including the Small Business Administration and the Department of Agriculture&mdash;which lends money to rural homebuyers&mdash;to change their underwriting practices so that unpaid medical debt doesn&rsquo;t hurt their chances of getting a loan.<span class=\"mntl-inline-citation mntl-dynamic-tooltip--trigger\" data-id=\"#citation-1\">1</span>&nbsp;The Department of Health and Human Services will also be examining reporting and collection practices of more than 2,000 healthcare providers, considering those findings for the first time when giving out federal grants.</p>\r\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-5\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\">\r\n<div id=\"mntl-block_11-0\" class=\"comp mntl-block\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-7\" class=\"comp text-passage mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\">The move adds to efforts to remove the harmful impacts that unpaid medical bills from doctors and hospitals can have on people&rsquo;s prospects for getting a loan, a job, or an apartment. Medical debt can reduce credit scores, but it doesn&rsquo;t tell lenders how reliable borrowers are when it comes to paying more typical bills because it&rsquo;s such an uncontrollable and unpredictable expense, according to research by the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau, the government&rsquo;s predatory lending watchdog.<span class=\"mntl-inline-citation mntl-dynamic-tooltip--trigger\" data-id=\"#citation-2\">2</span>&nbsp;The CFPB announced last month that it was evaluating whether medical debt should even be included on credit reports at all.<span class=\"mntl-inline-citation mntl-dynamic-tooltip--trigger\" data-id=\"#citation-3\">3</span></p>\r\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-8\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\">\r\n<div id=\"mntl-block_12-0\" class=\"comp mntl-block\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-10\" class=\"comp text-passage mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\">Last month, under pressure from the CFPB, the nation&rsquo;s three largest credit bureaus moved to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thebalance.com/credit-bureaus-to-ax-70-percent-of-medical-debt-from-reports-5222932\" data-component=\"link\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"internalLink\" data-ordinal=\"1\">blunt the impact of medical debt on their credit reports</a>, including by removing paid debts altogether and excluding any individual debts of under $500.</p>\r\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-11\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-13\" class=\"comp text-passage mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"><em>Have a question, comment, or story to share? You can reach Diccon at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:dhyatt@thebalance.com\" data-component=\"link\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"internalLink\" data-ordinal=\"1\">dhyatt@thebalance.com</a>.</em></p>\r\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-14\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0-16\" class=\"comp text-passage mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"><em>Want to read more content like this?&nbsp;<a href=\"https://link.about.com/join/3op/balance-today-article\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-component=\"link\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"externalLink\" data-ordinal=\"1\">Sign up</a>&nbsp;for The Balance&rsquo;s newsletter for daily insights, analysis, and financial tips, all delivered straight to your inbox every morning!</em></p>', ' ', '1649799710-biden.jpg', '1649799710-biden1.jpg', 'unpaid-medical-debt-loses-more-of-its-financial-stigma', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:11:50', 15),
(5, 22, '19, 17', 'Best small business loans of 2022', 'Are you a small business owner looking to find a loan to help you hire new talent, purchase equipment or inventory, or expand your business? Are you struggling to figure out which loan provider will meet your specific needs? Or, are you just totally overwhelmed with the number of choices and different options available? \r\n\r\nNo matter where you’re at in your small business loan search, read on, and see if you can find a small business loan that best fits your needs.', '<div class=\"header-wrapper\">\r\n<h2><span id=\"overview-of-the-best-small-business-loans\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">Overview of the best small business loans</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table id=\"tablepress-1014\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-1014 tablepress-responsive\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\r\n<th class=\"column-1\">Small business loan providers</th>\r\n<th class=\"column-2\">Best for</th>\r\n<th class=\"column-3\">Types of loans offered</th>\r\n<th class=\"column-4\">Max loan amount</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_1\" data-track=\"\">BlueVine</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">Invoice factoring</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">Invoice factoring, line of credit</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$5 million (factoring lines)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_2\" data-track=\"\">OnDeck</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">Access to fast funding</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">Term loans, line of credit</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$350,000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_3\" data-track=\"\">Live Oak</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">Personalized loan packages</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">SBA, USDA, commercial loans, and more</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$5.5 million</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_4\" data-track=\"\">Lendio</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">Comparing different loans</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">SBA, term loans, start-up loans, line of credit, and more</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$5.5 million</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_5\" data-track=\"\">SmartBiz</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">SBA loans</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">SBA loans, bank term loans</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$5.5 million</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"row-7 odd\">\r\n<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-business-loans-to-fund-your-new-venture#_6\" data-track=\"\">Kiva</a></td>\r\n<td class=\"column-2\">Micro loans</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-3\">Micro loans</td>\r\n<td class=\"column-4\">$15,000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"header-wrapper\">\r\n<h2 id=\"_1\"><span id=\"bluevine\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">BlueVine</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignright wp-image-88083 size-full\" src=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Blue_Vine_main_logo_210x100.jpg\" alt=\"Best Small Business Loans To Fund Your New Venture - BlueVine\" width=\"210\" height=\"100\" />BlueVine&nbsp;is an online fintech company that provides banking services and financing to small and medium-sized businesses. BlueVine was founded in 2013 and has since helped over 200,000 small business owners. When it comes to small business financing, BlueVine offers two different options: invoice factoring and lines of credit.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Through their invoice factoring service, small businesses can turn their unpaid invoices into working capital. Invoice factoring isn&rsquo;t exactly considered a loan, it&rsquo;s more like an advance on your invoices. So,&nbsp;<span class=\"shortcode\" data-alt=\"[wp_shortcode_190]\">BlueVine</span>&nbsp;advances your small business money, and then when your clients pay their invoices, the money goes to BlueVine.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To qualify for BlueVine factoring, you will need to meet the following requirements:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>530 +&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/credit-bureaus-credit-reports-credit-scores-fico-scores-whats-the-difference\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\">FICO score</a>.</li>\r\n<li>Be in business for a minimum of three months.</li>\r\n<li>$10,000 in monthly revenue.</li>\r\n<li>Must be a B2B.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Some key features of BlueVines invoice factoring services include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fast approval process &ndash; as little as 24 hours.</li>\r\n<li>Up to $5 million in factoring lines.</li>\r\n<li>Rates as low as 0.25% per week.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A BlueVine line of credit, on the other hand, grants&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-small-businesses-that-you-can-start-while-socially-distancing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\">your small business</a>&nbsp;the flexibility of a revolving line of credit. This means you can use what you need and only pay for the amount you use.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To qualify for BlueVine&rsquo;s line of credit, you will need to meet the following requirements:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minimum 650 FICO score.</li>\r\n<li>At least two years in business.</li>\r\n<li>$40,000 in monthly revenue.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Some key features of BlueVines line of credit service include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fast approval process &ndash; as little as five minutes.</li>\r\n<li>Credit lines up to $250,000.</li>\r\n<li>Rates as low as 4.7%.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In addition to its financing options, BlueVine also offers additional services to small businesses, like the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/bluevine-business-bank-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\">BlueVine checking account</a>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"header-wrapper\">\r\n<h2 id=\"_2\"><span id=\"ondeck\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">OnDeck</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ondeck.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-89743 alignright\" src=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ondeck_210x100.jpg\" alt=\"Best Small Business Loans To Fund Your New Venture - OnDeck\" width=\"210\" height=\"100\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.ondeck.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\">OnDeck</a>&nbsp;is another online lender that helps small businesses get the funding they need to grow and succeed. OnDeck was founded in 2006 and since this time it has extended $13 billion to small businesses. They offer two different types of small business loans: term loans and line of credit loans.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>OnDeck short term loans are a perfect option for small businesses that need money for a specific investment or purchase. OnDeck offers short term loans in the form of one-time lump sum payments. You then get to use the money as you see fit for your small business. You can work with OnDeck to find a repayment schedule that best fits your timeline.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To qualify for an OnDeck term loan, you will need to meet the following requirements:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Personal FICO score of 600.</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.moneyunder30.com/best-banks-for-small-businesses/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-track=\"\">Business bank account</a>.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum of one year in business.</li>\r\n<li>Annual revenue of $100K.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Some key features of OnDeck term loans include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Access to loan amounts from $5,000 to $250,000.</li>\r\n<li>Repayment terms up to 18 months.</li>\r\n<li>Automatic daily or weekly payments.</li>\r\n<li>Same day payments.</li>\r\n<li>Transparent pricing.</li>\r\n<li>SBA approved lender.</li>\r\n<li>Term loans rates as low as 11.98% APR.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>OnDeck&rsquo;s business lines of credit offer revolving loans that allow small business owners to access a fixed amount of capital that can be used exactly when it is needed.</p>\r\n<p>To qualify for OnDeck&rsquo;s line of credit, you will need to meet the same requirements as those for a term loan.</p>\r\n<p>Some key features of OnDeck line of credit include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Access to revolving credit.</li>\r\n<li>Access to the line of credit from $6,000 to $10,000.</li>\r\n<li>12-month repayment terms that reset after each withdrawal.</li>\r\n<li>Lines of Credit rates as low as 10.99% APR.</li>\r\n<li>Access to instant funding.</li>\r\n<li>No prepayment penalties.</li>\r\n</ul>', ' ', '1649799935-money.jpg', '1649799935-money1.jpg', 'best-small-business-loans-of-2022', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:15:35', 15);
INSERT INTO `blog_tbl` (`blog_id`, `category_id`, `tags_id`, `blog_name`, `short_desc`, `long_desc1`, `log_desc2`, `small_img`, `long_img`, `blog_url`, `blog_date`, `blog_status`, `blog_comment`, `featured`, `update_at`, `author_id`) VALUES
(6, 24, '19, 16, 12', 'How to Start a Blog That Generates $3817 a Month', 'Ever wondered how to start a blog and make enough money blogging to quit your job? \r\n\r\nYou can do it. Tons of people already have.\r\n\r\nWant definitive proof?\r\n\r\nThe blog you’re reading right now gets over 2,436,100 unique visitors a year and generates well over a million dollars in annual revenue.\r\n\r\nJust look at my revenue stats for a 30 day period:', '<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128695\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/neilpatel-revenue-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/neilpatel-revenue-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/neilpatel-revenue-how-to-start-a-blog-350x135.webp 350w\" alt=\"Neilpatel.com revenue chart for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"270\" /></figure>\r\n<p>$381,772 a month is a lot of money, especially for a blog. Now you aren&rsquo;t going to generate that much money, but it is realistic for you to make 1/100th of what I am making.</p>\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s why I&rsquo;m going to show you how to make $3817 a month.</p>\r\n<p>Making $300,000 per month is REALLY hard. Making $3000 per month is a lot easier.</p>\r\n<p>And for most folks, an extra $3000 per month would change their life.</p>\r\n<p>So, yes. Blocks of text and a handful of images can generate life-changing amounts of money.</p>\r\n<p>Want to know something else?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I started from the same place you&rsquo;re at right now. The only difference between you and me is that I&rsquo;ve already been doing this for a decade.</p>\r\n<p>Look, I stumbled a LOT along the way. Fell flat on my face. Had tons of terrible ideas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This guide shows you how to avoid the same mistakes I did. Not only will your path be easier, you&rsquo;ll get there a lot quicker.</p>\r\n<h2>Your 2-minute quick start cheat sheet</h2>\r\n<p>Looking for a barebones, quick start guide to get started as fast as possible? In this section, we won&rsquo;t cover everything, only the essential steps. Everything is covered in way more detail below, so jump down if you hit a snag.</p>\r\n<p>First head to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"><strong>Hostinger</strong></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"><strong>sign up for the WordPress Starter plan</strong></a>. It&rsquo;s just $3.99 per month and you will also&nbsp;<strong>get a free domain name</strong>&nbsp;with your hosting plan!</p>\r\n<p>Next, follow the instructions to set up your Hostinger account and now you officially have your own little piece of the internet.&nbsp;<strong>Congrats!</strong></p>\r\n<p>But, don&rsquo;t celebrate too hard just yet&mdash;we&rsquo;re not quite finished. From there, you need to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Install WordPress (your blogging platform)</li>\r\n<li>Choose and install a cheap/affordable theme</li>\r\n<li>Customize your new theme</li>\r\n<li>Write and publish your first blog post</li>\r\n<li>Stick to a regular publishing schedule</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>After you have your first few posts under your belt and traffic starts to flow in, you can start thinking about how you want to make your first $1.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>From selling ad space to digital/physical product offerings and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/what-is-affiliate-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">affiliate marketing</a>, there are dozens of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/8-powerful-ways-to-monetize-a-blog-that-generates-under-1000-visitors-per-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">monetization methods</a>&nbsp;you can explore.</p>\r\n<p>Now let&rsquo;s go through the whole process in detail. Here are the 10 steps to take:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-1\">Unleash ideas within you</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-2\">Choose a name for your new blog</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-3\">Get web hosting from Hostinger</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-4\">Get familiar with WordPress</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-5\">Install a WordPress Theme</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-6\">Customize Your Blog</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-7\">Brainstorm Blog Topics</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-8\">Write Your First Masterpiece</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-9\">Create an Editorial Calendar</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/how-to-start-a-blog/#step-10\">Monetize Your Blog</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-1\"><strong>Step 1. Unleash ideas within you</strong></h2>\r\n<p>If you want to&nbsp;create a blog, you don&rsquo;t need a revolutionary idea. But, your blog should be focused on something specific.</p>\r\n<p>Remember that no idea is&nbsp;<em>truly&nbsp;</em>unique, no matter how good it is.</p>\r\n<p>But you have unique&nbsp;<em>experiences</em>. You have a distinct voice. And you probably have a vibrant personality that will attract others who want to hear about your experiences.</p>\r\n<p>When it comes to choosing your blog&rsquo;s niche, there are two key questions to ask yourself.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>1. Do I Enjoy Learning About This Topic?</strong></h3>\r\n<p>If you don&rsquo;t love the topic, it&rsquo;ll show in your writing. You shouldn&rsquo;t even&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/outsource-blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">start a blog</a>&nbsp;if you don&rsquo;t love what you&rsquo;re&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/blogging-formula/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">blogging about.</a></p>\r\n<p>Whatever topic you pick, you need to love it and be naturally curious about it.</p>\r\n<p>If not,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/how-to-never-run-out-of-blog-post-ideas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">you&rsquo;ll run out of ideas quickly</a>. You&rsquo;ll lose any momentum you built up at the start.</p>\r\n<p>Most importantly, you won&rsquo;t be able to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/blogging-consistently/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">consistently create content</a>&nbsp;that will build your audience.</p>\r\n<p>If you are still lost, think about&nbsp;what sort of things people come to you for advice on. Do friends or family ask you for fitness tips? Recipe ideas? Career advice? You know what you can best speak to.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>2. Are Others Interested in The Same Things?</strong></h3>\r\n<p>You might feel like the only 20-something who&rsquo;s obsessed with knitting. But there are others out there.</p>\r\n<p>Do a quick Google search and you&rsquo;ll find over 1 million results aimed at people just like you.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-145257\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/young-knitters-search-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/young-knitters-search-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/young-knitters-search-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Young knitters Google search for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>You might be wondering if your idea is too quirky. Or, is it too broad? My advice is to get as focused as you can on something you&rsquo;re genuinely interested in.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to start a travel blog, for example, stay away from generic words like &ldquo;travel.&rdquo; Choose a more specific topic, like &ldquo;backpacking.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-2\">Step 2. Choose a name for your new blog</h2>\r\n<p>Now for the fun part: naming your blog.</p>\r\n<p>This is your brand. It&rsquo;s how people will remember you.</p>\r\n<p>But don&rsquo;t overthink it. The magic of a brand gets built over time. Even if you feel stuck, keep moving forward.</p>\r\n<p>The best way to land on the perfect name is to start with brainstorming. In the last step, we talked about unleashing all of your ideas and nailing down your niche.</p>\r\n<p>Now, it&rsquo;s time to take those ideas and turn them into a name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So, open up a new spreadsheet or grab a pen and paper. Then spend about ten minutes writing down every word that comes to mind.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>From there, start combining words and phrases until something stands out to you. Aim for 5 &ndash; 10 potential names and write them down.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Now, it&rsquo;s time to see if those names are available as domains. A domain is where your blog lives on the internet.</p>\r\n<p>As an example, neilpatel.com is my domain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Neil Patel is who I am, but it&rsquo;s also my brand and what you type into the address bar to find me. But that also means you can&rsquo;t use the domain because I already own it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You&nbsp;<em>could&nbsp;</em>do what I did and use your personal name as your domain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>But in most cases, I recommend choosing a different name for your blog. That&rsquo;ll make it a lot easier to sell the site if you ever want to.</p>\r\n<p>If none of your preferred site names are available as a .com, head back to the beginning and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/domain-name-unavailable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">keep brainstorming</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Here are some extra tips for choosing an excellent domain name:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Always choose a .com when possible</li>\r\n<li>Avoid using numbers, hyphens, and homophones (words that sounds the same but are spelled differently)</li>\r\n<li>Keep it as short and concise as possible</li>\r\n<li>Should be easy to say and understand</li>\r\n<li>Avoid complicated and commonly misspelled words</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>When you land on an available name, click next to automatically add it to your cart.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Don&rsquo;t buy it yet. I&rsquo;ll show you how to get your domain for free in the next step.&nbsp;</em></strong></p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-3\">Step 3. Get Web Hosting with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hostinger</a></h2>\r\n<p>Now it&rsquo;s time to get your blog live.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It may seem complicated at first, but don&rsquo;t worry. It&rsquo;s much easier than it sounds.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To get started, you need web hosting (where your blog lives) and a domain name (your blog&rsquo;s address). The good news is that&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hostinger</a>, my favorite web hosting company, offers both as a package deal.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"a1c85ac3 _9bd02324\">\r\n<div class=\"e5719e3b\">\r\n<div class=\"d9de5014\">\r\n<figure class=\"_7cb37961\"><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-logo.png\" alt=\"Hostinger\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /></a></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"_1dbf48e5\">\r\n<h3 class=\"d951d4b9\"><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hostinger</a></h3>\r\n<h4 class=\"d951d4b10\">Best Web Hosting</h4>\r\n<p class=\"_4ccf1904\">Get rock-solid web hosting at a steal of a price. Shared hosting that is perfect for your new blog starts as low as $1.99/month, or $3.99 per month if you want a free domain name. Plus, you can lock in that rate for four whole years!</p>\r\n<div class=\"cd35f914\"><a class=\"_2789f5c9\" href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Start today!</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Plus, it&rsquo;s incredibly affordable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Head over to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hostinger</a>&nbsp;and click &ldquo;Start Now.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Next, you&rsquo;ll see four different plans. Scroll down and select the WordPress Starter plan for $3.99/month. It includes everything you need when you&rsquo;re just getting started and is the lowest-cost plan that includes a free domain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>And you can always upgrade later if you need to.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/go/np0542/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"wp-image-143359\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-pricing-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-pricing-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-pricing-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger pricing page for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></a></figure>\r\n<p>If you want the best deal, opt for the four-year commitment. But you can also choose from one-year, two-year, and month-to-month terms.</p>\r\n<p>Next, you&rsquo;ll finish setting up your account.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143373\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-checkout-how-to-start-a-blog-2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-checkout-how-to-start-a-blog-2.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-checkout-how-to-start-a-blog-2-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger checkout page for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" />\r\n<figcaption>After your payment is processed, you&rsquo;ll be whisked away to Hostinger&rsquo;s hPanel, which will guide you through the rest of the setup process.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>First, select &ldquo;Myself&rdquo; when the wizard asks you who you&rsquo;re making the website for.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143361\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-guided-setup-part-2-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-guided-setup-part-2-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-guided-setup-part-2-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger guided setup step 2 for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>On the next screen, let the guide know that you&rsquo;re making a blog.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143362\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-start-blog-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-start-blog-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-start-blog-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>After that, you&rsquo;ll tell the wizard your level of comfort with building websites. I&rsquo;m pretty experienced, so I chose the second option.</p>\r\n<p>If you haven&rsquo;t created a blog from scratch more than once or twice, you might want to pick one of the two options on the right.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143363\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-experience-level-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-experience-level-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-experience-level-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger setup experience level How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" />\r\n<figcaption>Next, Hostinger will ask you which platform you want to use for your site. Select the WordPress option on the left.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>If you don&rsquo;t have a WordPress account already, Hostinger helpfully gives you a field to set an email address and password for one on the spot.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143364\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-wp-account-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-wp-account-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-wp-account-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve done that, you can select a blog template to start from. Or, you can start from scratch by clicking the text link at the bottom. If you&rsquo;re new to this, though, I&rsquo;d recommend starting with a template. There are a lot of gorgeously designed options to choose from.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143365\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-select-template-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-select-template-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-select-template-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger setup select template How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve made a decision there, you&rsquo;ll be able to buy a new domain or connect an existing one to your site.</p>\r\n<p>This will be easy since you already searched for available domains in Step 2. Click &ldquo;Select&rdquo; under Buy a Domain on the left, then enter your desired domain in the field that emerges below.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143366\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-domain-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-domain-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-domain-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Select the available domain and then make sure to add on WHOIS privacy for an extra $10 per year.</p>\r\n<p>It exists to keep your private information safe and secure. Without it, anyone can access your phone number, home address, and email.</p>\r\n<p>You still own the domain name, but your contact information is protected against scam callers and unsolicited mail.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s certainly worth the extra investment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>After that, you&rsquo;re done with the hardest part!&nbsp;<strong><em>Congrats on your new blog!</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>It will take just a few minutes for Hostinger to finish setting up your site. Stay on the screen until , you&rsquo;re ready to move on to the next step.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-4\"><strong>Step 4. Get Familiar with WordPress, Your Blogging Software</strong></h2>\r\n<p>You can&rsquo;t start a blog without blogging software. I run all of my blogs on WordPress because it&rsquo;s user-friendly, free, and powerful.</p>\r\n<p>If you decide to make a blog that&rsquo;s not on WordPress, you&rsquo;ll find that it is much more costly. WordPress offers a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/free-wordpress-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ton of free plugins</a>&nbsp;that allow you to modify your blog in any way, shape, or form.</p>\r\n<p>What&rsquo;s nice is that Hostinger takes care of WordPress installation for you during setup. You don&rsquo;t have to do anything to get it ready to use.</p>\r\n<p>After the Hostinger setup wizard is finished, you&rsquo;ll be greeted with a screen where you can connect your domain, view your site, or head to the WordPress dashboard or the Hostinger control panel.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143370\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-completed-setup-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-completed-setup-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-completed-setup-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger completed setup for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Click &ldquo;Manage WordPress&rdquo; and you&rsquo;ll be taken to that section in hPanel. Scroll down a bit and you&rsquo;ll see on the right the version of WordPress currently installed.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143369\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger WordPress version for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<p>If you ever have a issue, you can always do a clean installation of WordPress by clicking &ldquo;Install&rdquo; all the way at the bottom.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-143368\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-WP-install-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-WP-install-how-to-start-a-blog.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hostinger-WP-install-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.png 350w\" alt=\"Hostinger WordPress installation for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" /></figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-5\"><strong>Step 5. Design Your Blog With a WordPress Theme</strong></h2>\r\n<p>In the blogging world, pre-built&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/32-free-wordpress-themes-for-effective-content-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">WordPress site designs are called themes</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Out of the box, your WordPress blog will look something like this:</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128710\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WordPress-blank-site-how-to-start-a-blog-700x515.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WordPress-blank-site-how-to-start-a-blog-700x515.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WordPress-blank-site-how-to-start-a-blog-350x258.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WordPress-blank-site-how-to-start-a-blog-768x565.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WordPress-blank-site-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1069w\" alt=\"New blank WordPress site for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"515\" /></figure>\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s the simple foundation you start with. But you&rsquo;re going to want to find something that fits with your name, brand, and the experience you want readers to have.</p>\r\n<p>There are thousands of themes to choose from. But it can be easy to get trapped in &ldquo;shiny object syndrome&rdquo;, browsing through tons of pretty pictures and templates but not walking away with a theme that fits your needs.</p>\r\n<p>You can swap out your theme any time, so choose something that&rsquo;s good enough for now rather than stressing over the perfect option. Like your brand, your WordPress blog&rsquo;s theme will probably evolve over time as you figure out what works and looks best in practice.</p>\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s go through selecting a theme step by step.</p>\r\n<p>First, you need to log into your WordPress admin. You can access this by going to [yourdomain].com/wp-admin.</p>\r\n<p>Enter your user credentials to log in.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128711\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-login-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-login-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 610w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-login-how-to-start-a-blog-350x351.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-login-how-to-start-a-blog-175x175.webp 175w\" alt=\"WordPress login page for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"610\" height=\"612\" /></figure>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re new to WordPress, the dashboard might look a little daunting at first, but you&rsquo;ll be an expert with a little practice.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128794\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/wp-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog-700x500.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/wp-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog-700x500.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/wp-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog-350x250.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/wp-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog-768x549.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/wp-dashboard-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1114w\" alt=\"WordPress dashboard for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" /></figure>\r\n<p>To install a new theme, hover over the &ldquo;Appearance&rdquo; menu in the sidebar and click &ldquo;Themes.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128796\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-appearance-menu-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-appearance-menu-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 380w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-appearance-menu-how-to-start-a-blog-350x308.webp 350w\" alt=\"WordPress appearance menu for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"380\" height=\"334\" /></figure>\r\n<p>WordPress comes with a few themes ready to go, but we&rsquo;re going to search for the flashier premium themes that will make your eyes twinkle.</p>\r\n<p>Click the &ldquo;Add New&rdquo; button at the top to get access to thousands of WordPress themes.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128797\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-theme-how-to-start-a-blog-700x249.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-theme-how-to-start-a-blog-700x249.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-theme-how-to-start-a-blog-350x125.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-theme-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 719w\" alt=\"WordPress add new theme for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"249\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Your tastes and mine may be different. Fortunately, WordPress has a &ldquo;Feature Filter&rdquo; that lets you search for something that will fit your style.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128798\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filters-how-to-start-a-blog-700x282.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filters-how-to-start-a-blog-700x282.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filters-how-to-start-a-blog-350x141.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filters-how-to-start-a-blog-768x310.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filters-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1032w\" alt=\"WordPress theme filter for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"282\" /></figure>\r\n<p>The three categories are &ldquo;layout,&rdquo; &ldquo;features&rdquo; and &ldquo;subject.&rdquo; You can look for themes that closely hew to what your blog is going to be about or ones that have features you&rsquo;re already sure your blog will need.</p>\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s what your filter requests might look like.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128799\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filter-options-how-to-start-a-blog-700x260.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filter-options-how-to-start-a-blog-700x260.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filter-options-how-to-start-a-blog-350x130.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filter-options-how-to-start-a-blog-768x286.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-filter-options-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1221w\" alt=\"WordPress theme filter options for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"260\" /></figure>\r\n<p>After applying the filters, you&rsquo;ll see amazing themes that would otherwise cost thousands of dollars in design fees.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128800\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog-700x304.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog-700x304.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog-350x152.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog-768x334.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog-1536x667.webp 1536w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-options-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1681w\" alt=\"WordPress theme options for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"304\" /></figure>\r\n<p>If you click on the theme&rsquo;s thumbnail, you can get an instant preview of what your blog will look like. Evaluate if it fits both your personal style and the topic that you&rsquo;ll be covering.</p>\r\n<p>Once you&rsquo;re satisfied with the sneak peek, click the &ldquo;Install&rdquo; button.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128801\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog-700x265.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog-700x265.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog-350x132.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog-768x290.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog-1536x581.webp 1536w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-preview-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1891w\" alt=\"WordPress theme preview for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"265\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Once the installation is complete, click the &ldquo;Activate&rdquo; button and you&rsquo;re all set.</p>\r\n<p>If you can&rsquo;t find a theme that you like, there are premium themes that you can purchase from sites like:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Themeforest</li>\r\n<li>Elegant Themes</li>\r\n<li>StudioPress</li>\r\n<li>Thrive Themes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>By now, your theme should be activated and ready to go. Let&rsquo;s move on to customizing your theme.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-6\"><strong>Step 6. Customize and Optimize Your WordPress Blog</strong></h2>\r\n<p>There are endless customization choices that you can make on a WordPress blog. We&rsquo;ll stick with the essentials.</p>\r\n<p>Themes are the foundation of your design and include the core functionalities. WordPress also has plugins that can add to or extend the functionality of your blog in impressive ways.</p>\r\n<p>There are WordPress plugins for everything from adding ecommerce functionality or contact forms to your site to analyzing your content for SEO improvements (more on that in a bit) or boosting site security and performance.</p>\r\n<p>The first step is to click the &ldquo;Customize&rdquo; button on your active theme.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128802\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-customization-how-to-start-a-blog-700x355.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-customization-how-to-start-a-blog-700x355.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-customization-how-to-start-a-blog-350x177.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-customization-how-to-start-a-blog-768x389.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-customization-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 850w\" alt=\"Customize WordPress theme for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"355\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Menu options in the sidebar will vary, depending on the theme you choose. The main category to edit is &ldquo;Site Identity.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128803\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog-700x322.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog-700x322.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog-350x161.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog-768x354.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog-1536x707.webp 1536w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-site-identity-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1898w\" alt=\"WordPress theme site identity for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"322\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Here, you can add the name of your blog and a tagline if you wish. When you&rsquo;re done, click the &ldquo;Save and Publish&rdquo; button.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128804\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-save-and-publish-how-to-start-a-blog-700x563.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-save-and-publish-how-to-start-a-blog-700x563.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-save-and-publish-how-to-start-a-blog-350x282.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-save-and-publish-how-to-start-a-blog-768x618.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-theme-save-and-publish-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 828w\" alt=\"Save and publish customized WordPress theme for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"563\" /></figure>\r\n<h3><strong>Optimize for Search Engine Traffic</strong></h3>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/what-is-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Search engine optimization (SEO)</a>&nbsp;is a multi-billion dollar industry.</p>\r\n<p>SEO is the process of optimizing your website to be found in search engines for particular keywords and phrases.</p>\r\n<p>I attribute a good portion of my success to being easily discoverable for relevant search terms, which has helped me build my networks and net worth.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re new to SEO, then this may seem daunting.</p>\r\n<p>But, WordPress makes it insanely simple to optimize the technical aspects of your blog.</p>\r\n<p>The majority of your SEO efforts will be to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/ultimate-guide-to-creating-content/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">create engaging content for real people</a>. Whether that&rsquo;s through text,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/video-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">videos</a>, or images, your job as a blogger is to spark a relationship with your readers.</p>\r\n<p>And, what better way is there than through relatable and informative conversation?</p>\r\n<p>You can get started by downloading a plugin called&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/setup-yoast-seo-wordpress-correctly/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Yoast SEO</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Hover over the plugins menu on the side and click &ldquo;Add New.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128805\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-plugin-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 636px) 100vw, 636px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-plugin-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 636w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/WP-add-new-plugin-how-to-start-a-blog-350x462.webp 350w\" alt=\"Add new WordPress plugin for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"636\" height=\"839\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Search for &ldquo;Yoast SEO&rdquo; in the search bar and it will be the first result that comes up.</p>\r\n<p>Click the &ldquo;Install Now&rdquo; button. Then, hit the &ldquo;Activate&rdquo; button once the installation is complete.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128806\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog-700x202.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog-700x202.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog-350x101.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog-768x222.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog-1536x444.webp 1536w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-for-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1697w\" alt=\"Yoast SEO plugin for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"202\" /></figure>\r\n<p>You can access the plugin&rsquo;s settings from the new SEO menu in the sidebar or by clicking the icon at the top.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128807\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-plugin-icon-how-to-start-a-blog-700x354.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-plugin-icon-how-to-start-a-blog-700x354.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-plugin-icon-how-to-start-a-blog-350x177.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-plugin-icon-how-to-start-a-blog-768x388.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-plugin-icon-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1254w\" alt=\"Yoast SEO plugin icon for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"354\" /></figure>\r\n<p>From the dashboard, go to &ldquo;Your Info&rdquo; and set the foundations for your blog.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128808\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-your-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-700x530.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-your-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-700x530.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-your-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-350x265.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-your-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-768x582.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-your-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 879w\" alt=\"Yoast SEO insert your site info for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"530\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Make sure that your website name and tagline are correct. Then, identify yourself as a company or person.</p>\r\n<p>Click the &ldquo;Save Changes&rdquo; button and we&rsquo;ll move on to the next step.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128809\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-700x656.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-700x656.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog-350x328.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-site-info-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 756w\" alt=\"Enter site info for Yoast SEO for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"656\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Next, go to the &ldquo;Webmaster Tools&rdquo; tab and click &ldquo;Google Search Console.&rdquo; Google Search Console is a webmaster tool that allows you to submit your site to their search index and optimize visibility.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128810\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-Google-verification-how-to-start-a-blog-700x624.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-Google-verification-how-to-start-a-blog-700x624.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-Google-verification-how-to-start-a-blog-350x312.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-SEO-Google-verification-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 715w\" alt=\"Verify Yoast SEO for Google Search for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"624\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Sign into your Google account, whether that&rsquo;s your Gmail or Drive account.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128811\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/google-login-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/google-login-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 655w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/google-login-how-to-start-a-blog-350x320.webp 350w\" alt=\"Google login screen for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"655\" height=\"598\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Once you&rsquo;ve logged in, click the &ldquo;Alternate methods&rdquo; tab and select &ldquo;HTML tag.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128812\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Google-Search-Console-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Google-Search-Console-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Google-Search-Console-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog-350x211.webp 350w\" alt=\"HTML tag in Google Search Console for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"421\" /></figure>\r\n<p>A new drop-down will appear with your search console meta code. Copy the alphanumeric string without the quotation marks.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128813\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/copy-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog-700x200.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/copy-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog-700x200.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/copy-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog-350x100.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/copy-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog-768x220.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/copy-HTML-tag-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 905w\" alt=\"copy tag in Google Search Console for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"200\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Next, paste your meta code into the Google Search Console text box and click &ldquo;Save Changes.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128814\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verify-Google-in-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 681px) 100vw, 681px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verify-Google-in-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 681w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/verify-Google-in-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog-350x225.webp 350w\" alt=\"Verify Google Search Console in Yoast SEO plugin for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"681\" height=\"438\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Finally, click the &ldquo;Verify&rdquo; button.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-128815\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Verify-button-in-Yoast-SEO-how-to-start-a-blog-700x369.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Verify-button-in-Yoast-SEO-how-to-start-a-blog-700x369.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Verify-button-in-Yoast-SEO-how-to-start-a-blog-350x184.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Verify-button-in-Yoast-SEO-how-to-start-a-blog-768x404.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Verify-button-in-Yoast-SEO-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1077w\" alt=\"Click verify in Yoast SEO for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"369\" /></figure>\r\n<p>As you tinker around in Webmaster Central, you&rsquo;ll gain a wealth of data-driven insight, such as keyword phrases you rank for, errors on your blog, and the ability to give Google a nudge when you publish a new post.</p>\r\n<p>Next, go to the &ldquo;General&rdquo; tab and start the installation wizard.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-128816\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-installation-wizard-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-installation-wizard-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 653w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-installation-wizard-how-to-start-a-blog-350x344.webp 350w\" alt=\"Yoast SEO wizard for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"653\" height=\"642\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Yoast will take you through a series of 10 quick steps to optimize your WordPress blog.</p>\r\n<p>The first step is a welcome screen that you can skip.</p>\r\n<p>In the second step, select the environment that best suits your site. Most likely, you&rsquo;ll choose the production environment, which means that it is a real website that you intend on driving traffic to.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-129490\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-optim-environment-how-to-start-a-blog-700x413.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-optim-environment-how-to-start-a-blog-700x413.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-optim-environment-how-to-start-a-blog-350x206.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-optim-environment-how-to-start-a-blog-768x453.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Yoast-optim-environment-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 784w\" alt=\"Yoast optimization process environment step for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"413\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Step 3 is the website type. Choose blog and click next.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132711\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-site-type-how-to-start-a-blog-700x491.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-site-type-how-to-start-a-blog-700x491.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-site-type-how-to-start-a-blog-350x246.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-site-type-how-to-start-a-blog-768x539.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-site-type-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 781w\" alt=\"Yoast SEO optimization for site type for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"491\" /></figure>\r\n<p>The next step is to set yourself up as a company or person. We already set this up before, so you can skip this step.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132712\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-company-or-individual-how-to-start-a-blog-700x479.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-company-or-individual-how-to-start-a-blog-700x479.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-company-or-individual-how-to-start-a-blog-350x239.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-company-or-individual-how-to-start-a-blog-768x526.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-company-or-individual-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 776w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"479\" /></figure>\r\n<p>In step 5, you can add any social profiles that are associated with your blog. Click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; when complete.</p>\r\n<p>Step 6 is about post visibility. The default settings are fine to use. Set your &ldquo;Posts&rdquo; and &ldquo;Pages&rdquo; to visible and &ldquo;Media&rdquo; to hidden.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132713\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-post-visibility-how-to-start-a-blog-700x748.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-post-visibility-how-to-start-a-blog-700x748.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-post-visibility-how-to-start-a-blog-350x374.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-post-visibility-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 766w\" alt=\"Set post type visibility in Yoast SEO for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"748\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Next, you&rsquo;ll have to decide whether you&rsquo;ll have multiple authors or a solo blogger. If you choose to add another writer in the future, you can change these settings later.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132714\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog-700x389.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog-700x389.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog-350x195.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog-768x427.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog-460x255.webp 460w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-authors-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 779w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"389\" /></figure>\r\n<p>If you wish to have the Yoast SEO plugin pull in data from Google&rsquo;s search console, step 8 is the place to do it.</p>\r\n<p>Click on the &ldquo;Get Google Authorization Code&rdquo; button.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132715\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-Google-Search-Console-connect-how-to-start-a-blog-700x482.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-Google-Search-Console-connect-how-to-start-a-blog-700x482.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-Google-Search-Console-connect-how-to-start-a-blog-350x241.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-Google-Search-Console-connect-how-to-start-a-blog-768x529.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-Google-Search-Console-connect-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 777w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"482\" /></figure>\r\n<p>A new pop-up will appear where you can allow Yoast to access your search console data. Click the &ldquo;Allow&rdquo; button to confirm access.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132716\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Google-auth-for-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Google-auth-for-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 600w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Google-auth-for-Yoast-how-to-start-a-blog-350x257.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"440\" /></figure>\r\n<p>In step 9, you can verify your website name and choose a title separator.</p>\r\n<p>The title separator is a symbol used to separate your blog post&rsquo;s title and your website&rsquo;s name in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/title-tags-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">meta title information</a>. This is what Google searchers will see when finding your blog through a search query.</p>\r\n<p>For instance, if you found this post on Google, you might have seen &ldquo;How to Start a Blog &ndash; Neil Patel.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>The symbol is a matter of personal preference. Click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; when you&rsquo;re ready to move on.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132717\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-title-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x607.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-title-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x607.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-title-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-350x303.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-title-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-768x666.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-optim-title-settings-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 782w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"607\" /></figure>\r\n<p>The final step is no step at all. It&rsquo;s a congratulatory message confirming that you have successfully optimized your SEO settings for your budding WordPress blog.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>XML Sitemaps</strong></h4>\r\n<p>The last Yoast SEO setting worth configuring is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/xml-sitemap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">an XML sitemap</a>. An XML sitemap is a file that lists the URLs for your website.</p>\r\n<p>It helps Google and other search engines crawl your site for new posts and pages. Fortunately, Yoast has a built-in feature that automatically updates your sitemap, so you can click it and forget it.</p>\r\n<p>In the &ldquo;Features&rdquo; tab, set the &ldquo;Advanced settings pages&rdquo; to &ldquo;Enabled&rdquo; and save the changes.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132718\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-advanced-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x617.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-advanced-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x617.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-advanced-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-350x309.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-advanced-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-768x677.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-advanced-settings-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 887w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"617\" /></figure>\r\n<p>A new group of menus will appear in the sidebar, under &ldquo;SEO.&rdquo; Select the &ldquo;XML Sitemaps&rdquo; menu.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132719\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-SEO-xml-sitemaps-how-to-start-a-blog-700x224.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-SEO-xml-sitemaps-how-to-start-a-blog-700x224.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-SEO-xml-sitemaps-how-to-start-a-blog-350x112.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-SEO-xml-sitemaps-how-to-start-a-blog-768x245.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-SEO-xml-sitemaps-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1265w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"224\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Select the &ldquo;User Sitemap&rdquo; tab and toggle &ldquo;Author / user sitemap&rdquo; to enabled. Don&rsquo;t forget to save your changes.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132720\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-user-sitemap-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x421.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-user-sitemap-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-700x421.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-user-sitemap-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-350x210.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-user-sitemap-settings-how-to-start-a-blog-768x462.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-user-sitemap-settings-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 815w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"421\" /></figure>\r\n<p>You can play around with these settings endlessly, but everything that we&rsquo;ve set up to this point will get you started on the right track.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Set Up Permalinks</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Permalinks are static hyperlinks that lead to a particular blog post or page. By default, WordPress automatically generates permalinks when you create a post, with the post ID number coming after your domain.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132721\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-default-permaklink-how-to-start-a-blog-700x550.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-default-permaklink-how-to-start-a-blog-700x550.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-default-permaklink-how-to-start-a-blog-350x275.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-default-permaklink-how-to-start-a-blog-768x603.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-default-permaklink-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 796w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"550\" /></figure>\r\n<p>The permalink &ldquo;/p=1213&rdquo; is in no way sexy and it doesn&rsquo;t help anyone understand what the page is about before viewing it.</p>\r\n<p>The simple fix is to set a permalink structure.</p>\r\n<p>In the left sidebar, mouse-over &ldquo;Settings&rdquo; and choose &ldquo;Permalinks.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132724\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-settings-permalinks-how-to-start-a-blog-700x251.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-settings-permalinks-how-to-start-a-blog-700x251.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-settings-permalinks-how-to-start-a-blog-350x126.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-settings-permalinks-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 758w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"251\" /></figure>\r\n<p>There are a few options to choose from. I use the &ldquo;Post name&rdquo; structure on my blog which uses keywords from my title to create a unique permalink.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132726\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-set-post-name-permalink-for-how-to-start-a-blog-700x404.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-set-post-name-permalink-for-how-to-start-a-blog-700x404.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-set-post-name-permalink-for-how-to-start-a-blog-350x202.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-set-post-name-permalink-for-how-to-start-a-blog-768x444.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-set-post-name-permalink-for-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 985w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"404\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Save the settings after you&rsquo;ve selected it. You&rsquo;ll see this in action a bit later.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re still with me, you&rsquo;ve purchased your domain and web hosting, installed a theme, and optimized your website to be crawled and found by search engines.</p>\r\n<p>Now, we get to the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/blogging-formula/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">bread and butter of blogging</a>. What are you going to write about in your blog?</p>\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s find out.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-7\"><strong>Step 7. Brainstorm Blog Topics</strong></h2>\r\n<p>On the technical side, your blog is all set up and ready to go. When it comes to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/generate-content-ideas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">topic generation</a>, the world is your oyster.</p>\r\n<p>The majority of your blog posts will come from personal experiences, passions, successes, failures, and new learnings.</p>\r\n<p>People use questions as search queries, like:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>What should I write about?</li>\r\n<li>What to blog about?</li>\r\n<li>Should I start blogging?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>So naturally, you should start off with some questions of your own. I use a series of questions and a systematic process to come up with my blog topic ideas.</p>\r\n<p>No need to worry. It&rsquo;s not complicated and it won&rsquo;t take very much time.</p>\r\n<p>By following this process, you should be able to come up with about 50 working topics within a half hour of distraction-free time.</p>\r\n<p>Pull out a pen and paper or open up your favorite word processing tool.</p>\r\n<p>The goal of this exercise is to get 10 answers for each question. If you can think of more, note them all.</p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s time to look through the lens of your readers with these 5 questions.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>1. &ldquo;What Excites, Intrigues, or Stirs Passion in My Readers?&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Examples:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>As a golfer, I get excited by hitting my driver farther. I&rsquo;m fascinated by mental performance. I&rsquo;m passionate about healthy living.</li>\r\n<li>As a new stay-at-home mom, I get excited by budget-friendly ideas for the family. I&rsquo;m intrigued by sleep-training. I&rsquo;m passionate about homeschooling.</li>\r\n<li>As an avid camper, I get excited about finding undervalued camping sites. I&rsquo;m intrigued by survival tactics. I&rsquo;m passionate about minimalist living.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>2. &ldquo;What Common Challenges Do My Readers Face?&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Examples:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Golfers might struggle with slicing the ball.</li>\r\n<li>Stay-at-home moms may find meal planning challenging.</li>\r\n<li>Campers might struggle with packing light.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>3. &ldquo;What Character Traits Do My Readers Possess?</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Example:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Serious golfers have emotional stability.</li>\r\n<li>Moms are patient and have a sense of humor.</li>\r\n<li>Campers are adventurous and resourceful.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>4. &ldquo;What Do My Readers Love About My Niche?&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Example:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Golfers love the challenge of perfection.</li>\r\n<li>Stay-at-home moms love being a part of their child&rsquo;s mental, physical and emotional development.</li>\r\n<li>Campers love time away from the busy city life.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>5. &ldquo;What Do My Readers Hate About My Niche?&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Examples:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Golfers hate playing with partners who complain all day long.</li>\r\n<li>Stay-at-home moms hate being looked down on by others.</li>\r\n<li>Campers hate getting eaten alive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You get the point. Now that you have about 50 answers, you can begin dissecting blog post ideas from each answer. The sky is the limit.</p>\r\n<p>Here are a few examples you can extract from one answer in your list:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cure Your Slice: The Foolproof Guide To Hit The Fairway Every Time</li>\r\n<li>3 Reasons Why You&rsquo;re Slicing The Ball And One Stupid Simple Fix</li>\r\n<li>Never Slice Again: 9 Drills To Play Like The Pros</li>\r\n<li>7 Training Aids For Dead Straight Ball Flight</li>\r\n<li>How To Shoot Even Par With A Nasty Slice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Try to come up with a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/the-step-by-step-guide-to-writing-powerful-headlines/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">catchy headline that will draw your readers</a>&nbsp;in and then throw them a one-two punch in the rest of your content.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"rll-youtube-player\" data-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wDuL4N1Gi5g\" data-id=\"wDuL4N1Gi5g\" data-query=\"feature=oembed\">\r\n<div data-id=\"wDuL4N1Gi5g\" data-query=\"feature=oembed\" data-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wDuL4N1Gi5g\"><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wDuL4N1Gi5g/sddefault.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /><button class=\"play\" aria-label=\"play Youtube video\"></button></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-8\"><strong>Step 8. Write Your First Masterpiece</strong></h2>\r\n<p>WordPress uses an intuitive editor, similar to your favorite word processing tools. New blog entries can be created directly from your WordPress admin dashboard.</p>\r\n<p>Click on &ldquo;Posts&rdquo; in the left sidebar.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132727\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-posts-on-sidebar-how-to-start-a-blog-700x437.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-posts-on-sidebar-how-to-start-a-blog-700x437.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-posts-on-sidebar-how-to-start-a-blog-350x218.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-posts-on-sidebar-how-to-start-a-blog-768x479.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/WP-posts-on-sidebar-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 906w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"437\" /></figure>\r\n<p>This will populate a list of your blog entries in descending order. Since we&rsquo;re working with a fresh install, you won&rsquo;t see anything here.</p>\r\n<p>To create a new entry, click the &ldquo;Add New&rdquo; button at the top or in the sidebar.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132728\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-new-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x409.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-new-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x409.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-new-post-how-to-start-a-blog-350x205.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-new-post-how-to-start-a-blog-768x449.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-new-post-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 922w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"409\" /></figure>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll be brought to the editor and you can begin blogging.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132729\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-post-editor-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-post-editor-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-post-editor-how-to-start-a-blog-350x171.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"342\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Click on the + in the right corner to see WordPress&rsquo;s Gutenberg blocks, which allow you to add headings, media, quotes, and tons of other features to your blog.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132730\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-block-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-block-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-block-how-to-start-a-blog-350x224.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"447\" /></figure>\r\n<p>First things first; add one of the titles that you developed in your brainstorming session in the title text box.</p>\r\n<p>Once you save this post as a draft, WordPress will create a permalink based on the keywords used in your title.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-149287\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x372.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x372.png 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog-350x186.png 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog-768x408.png 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog-1536x815.png 1536w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/np-test-golf-post-how-to-start-a-blog.png 1541w\" alt=\"WordPress title and permalink in post draft for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"372\" /></figure>\r\n<p>You can start typing the body of your article in the large text area and write until you feel happy with your content.</p>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll want to add visual assets to your blog posts as well. Images help engage readers and can often illustrate concepts better than words.</p>\r\n<p>To add new images, ensure that your text cursor is in the place where you want your image to appear. Click the blue + sign, then select the &ldquo;Image&rdquo; block.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132732\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-image-block-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-image-block-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 659w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-add-image-block-how-to-start-a-blog-350x322.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"659\" height=\"607\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Choose &ldquo;upload&rdquo; or select the image from your Media Library if its already uploaded to your site.</p>\r\n<p>After your image has uploaded, you can resize it, and add links using the icons at the top of the image.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132733\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-image-crop-and-edit-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-image-crop-and-edit-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/wp-image-crop-and-edit-how-to-start-a-blog-350x223.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"446\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Your image will automatically insert into your post.</p>\r\n<p>After you&rsquo;ve completed your article, you&rsquo;ll need to make a few last minute optimizations using the Yoast SEO plugin.</p>\r\n<p>Yoast has post specific settings that can be at the bottom of the main text area.</p>\r\n<p>The fur main settings are &ldquo;SEO title,&rdquo;&ldquo;slug,&rdquo; &ldquo;meta description&rdquo; and &ldquo;focus keyphrases.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>Completing these settings will generate a preview of what your post will look like when it is discovered in Google&rsquo;s search engine results.</p>\r\n<p>Create SEO titles that are attractive to click and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/how-to-write-meta-descriptions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">meta descriptions</a>&nbsp;that explain what your post is about.</p>\r\n<p>The Yoast SEO plugin will provide real-time feedback, as you begin to optimize your title and description.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132734\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-feedback-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-700x497.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-feedback-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-700x497.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-feedback-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-350x248.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-feedback-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-768x545.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Yoast-feedback-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 946w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"497\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Aim for as many green lights as possible, but don&rsquo;t stress if you&rsquo;re unable to get a perfect score. If you can get 80% green lights, then you&rsquo;re on the right track.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132735\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-analysis-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-700x381.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-analysis-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-700x381.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-analysis-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-350x191.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-analysis-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog-768x418.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/yoast-analysis-in-wp-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 946w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Before you publish your post, you can view what your blog post will look like by clicking the &ldquo;preview&rdquo; button at the top of the page.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-149290\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/preview-post-how-to-start-a-blog.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/preview-post-how-to-start-a-blog.png 646w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/preview-post-how-to-start-a-blog-350x328.png 350w\" alt=\"Preview post draft in WordPress for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"646\" height=\"605\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Before you hit that publish button, you want to make sure that your entry looks and feels the way that you want it to.</p>\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s a quick checklist to consider, before you hit the publish button:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Speak in a conversational tone.</li>\r\n<li>Content flows naturally.</li>\r\n<li>Easy on the eyes with adequate white space.</li>\r\n<li>Use&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/headings-impact-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">headings</a>&nbsp;to separate sections.</li>\r\n<li>Bullet points and lists.</li>\r\n<li>Check for typos and grammatical errors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If everything checks out, you&rsquo;re ready to publish your first blog post.</p>\r\n<p>Scroll to the top of the page and click the publish button that&rsquo;s just to the right of the preview button to have your post go live immediately.</p>\r\n<p>And here&rsquo;s what my final post looks like.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132738\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x390.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog-700x390.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog-350x195.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog-768x428.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog-460x255.webp 460w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Finished-and-uploaded-WP-post-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 1523w\" alt=\"WordPress post post-publish for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"390\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Congratulations. You&rsquo;ve successfully set up a blog that looks great and is optimized for search engine traffic. Feels good right?</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-9\"><strong>Step 9. Create an Editorial Calendar</strong></h2>\r\n<p>One of the fatal mistakes I see bloggers make is to blog only when they &ldquo;feel like it.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>They forget that new fans want more content and they fail to deliver.</p>\r\n<p>Unforeseen circumstances will arise. You&rsquo;ll let a new Netflix series take over the time that you could have spent blogging.</p>\r\n<p>Life will continue to throw curveballs at you, whether you start blogging or not.</p>\r\n<p>Consistency is undervalued and it needs to be something you prioritize.</p>\r\n<p>I&rsquo;ve written over a thousand articles and it&rsquo;s not because I type 7,000 words per minute.</p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s because I&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/create-editorial-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">follow an editorial calendar without compromise.</a></p>\r\n<p>Schedules aren&rsquo;t just for big publications like The New York Times and the Huffington Post. They&rsquo;re for regular people like you and me.</p>\r\n<p>Think about it like this.</p>\r\n<p>If you have a doctor&rsquo;s appointment in your calendar or even a lunch date with a friend, you&rsquo;re going to honor it. Worst case scenario, you&rsquo;ll reschedule for the next available time-slot.</p>\r\n<p>Editorial calendars work in a similar fashion.</p>\r\n<p>They make aggressive goals reachable in micro-steps. They keep you organized. They streamline your social media and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/beginners-guide-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">email marketing efforts</a>.</p>\r\n<p>And, you&rsquo;ll be surprised at how an editorial calendar can even help you grow in character and integrity.</p>\r\n<p>We are creatures of habit.</p>\r\n<p>The better you keep your dates, the faster you&rsquo;ll grow your audience.</p>\r\n<p>So, how do you get started and how much will it cost?</p>\r\n<p>Nada.</p>\r\n<p>Just open up a new Excel spreadsheet. If you have multiple writers, you can share the sheet using Google drive.</p>\r\n<p>Start with four columns &ndash; Publishing Date, Title, Keyword and Notes.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132740\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Editorial-calendar-example-how-to-start-a-blog-700x187.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Editorial-calendar-example-how-to-start-a-blog-700x187.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Editorial-calendar-example-how-to-start-a-blog-350x93.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Editorial-calendar-example-how-to-start-a-blog-768x205.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Editorial-calendar-example-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 927w\" alt=\"Example editorial calendar for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"187\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Your needs might be different than mine, so feel free to add additional columns as needed. Common additions might include &ldquo;Author,&rdquo;&rdquo;Category&rdquo; and &ldquo;Persona.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>The simpler you keep it, the easier it will be to digest and follow.</p>\r\n<p>Look through your calendar on your iPhone, Android, or the one hanging on your fridge. How often can you post?</p>\r\n<p>Monthly? Weekly? Daily?</p>\r\n<p>Be conservative with your goals, because consistently missing deadlines can lead to quitting altogether.</p>\r\n<p>Next, go through the answers that you came up with in your brainstorming session and add them under the &ldquo;Title&rdquo; column.</p>\r\n<p>Your titles don&rsquo;t need to be perfect yet. Throw in a working headline that you can spruce up before publishing.</p>\r\n<p>Sometimes, the best headlines come after you&rsquo;ve written your article. You&rsquo;ll have a crystal clear picture of what your story is about and who it is for.</p>\r\n<p>The &ldquo;Keyword&rdquo; column is intended for SEO purposes. If you&rsquo;re targeting&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/right-keywords-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">specific keyword phrases</a>&nbsp;that you&rsquo;d like to rank for, add those in there.</p>\r\n<p>If nothing comes to mind, you can do some keyword research later on.</p>\r\n<p>Finally, there&rsquo;s the &ldquo;Notes&rdquo; column.</p>\r\n<p>This section is a perfect place to write down brilliant ideas that come to mind. Notes also act as a great tool to stay focused on the topic at hand and tackle it coherently.</p>\r\n<p>You should be able to write up a set of 25 blog post topics with deadlines that you&rsquo;re confident about keeping.</p>\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s almost half a year&rsquo;s worth of blog posts for a weekly writer.</p>\r\n<p>Okay. You have the editorial, but you&rsquo;re still&nbsp;<em>missing the calendar.</em></p>\r\n<p>Go to Google Calendars and set up a new calendar. You can do this by clicking the down arrow to the right of &ldquo;My Calendars.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img class=\"wp-image-132741\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/set-up-Google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/set-up-Google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 556w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/set-up-Google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog-350x337.webp 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"556\" height=\"535\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Click &ldquo;Create New Calendar&rdquo; and add a name, description and time zone. You can share this calendar with other participants on your team.</p>\r\n<p>If you don&rsquo;t have team members, share it with your spouse or a good friend who is willing to keep you accountable to your goals.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132743\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/create-new-google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog-700x558.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/create-new-google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog-700x558.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/create-new-google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog-350x279.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/create-new-google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog-768x612.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/create-new-google-calendar-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 938w\" alt=\"Create new Google calendar for How to Start a Blog\" width=\"700\" height=\"558\" /></figure>\r\n<p>After you&rsquo;ve filled out the essential information, click &ldquo;Create Calendar&rdquo; and get acquainted with your new best friend.</p>\r\n<p>Make sure that your calendar is selected in the left sidebar and change your schedule view to weekly.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132744\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-weekly-view-how-to-start-a-blog-700x416.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-weekly-view-how-to-start-a-blog-700x416.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-weekly-view-how-to-start-a-blog-350x208.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-weekly-view-how-to-start-a-blog-768x457.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-weekly-view-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 829w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"416\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Click on a time slot under a day and add your blog post title as the &ldquo;Event Title.&rdquo; I recommend that you set a notification for a couple of days before the publishing date.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-132746\" src=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-timeslot-how-to-start-a-blog-700x316.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-timeslot-how-to-start-a-blog-700x316.webp 700w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-timeslot-how-to-start-a-blog-350x158.webp 350w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-timeslot-how-to-start-a-blog-768x347.webp 768w, https://neilpatel.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/google-calendar-timeslot-how-to-start-a-blog.webp 991w\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"316\" /></figure>\r\n<p>If you only write whenever it&rsquo;s convenient, you&rsquo;re heading down a dangerous road.</p>\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ll eventually run out of ideas, lose motivation and forget about the drive you once had to start your own blog.</p>\r\n<p>Editorial calendars are a quick fix for a blogger&rsquo;s procrastination.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"step-10\"><strong>Step 10. Monetize Your Blog</strong></h2>\r\n<p>The last step is to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/8-powerful-ways-to-monetize-a-blog-that-generates-under-1000-visitors-per-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">monetize your blog</a>. You may not have a desire to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/8-powerful-ways-to-monetize-a-blog-that-generates-under-1000-visitors-per-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">monetize your blog</a>&nbsp;immediately. If that&rsquo;s you, then it&rsquo;s a good thing.</p>\r\n<p>Hear me out.</p>\r\n<p>Conventional styles of selling looked something like this:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Think of an idea.</li>\r\n<li>Create a product.</li>\r\n<li>Try and sell the product.</li>\r\n<li>File for bankruptcy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This method has been unsuccessful for so many individuals and businesses, because they didn&rsquo;t&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/establishing-audience-loyalty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">build an audience</a>&nbsp;before creating it.</p>\r\n<p>They based market demand off &ldquo;gut feelings.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>And, that&rsquo;s why blogging is the perfect channel for monetization.</p>\r\n<p>You can build an audience through various mediums, like your email newsletter, blog comments, and social media channels.</p>\r\n<h3>Ask your audience</h3>\r\n<p>Blogging allows people into your life. If you think of your favorite bloggers, you might feel like you know them on a somewhat personal level.</p>\r\n<p>Also, your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/read-your-audiences-mind/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">market research</a>&nbsp;becomes significantly easier. I ask questions at the end of my blog posts that generate hundreds of comments.</p>', ' ', '1649800599-blog.jpg', '1649800599-blog1.jpg', 'how-to-start-a-blog-that-generates-3817-a-month', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:26:39', 15);
