(7, 23, '18, 15', 'GUEST COLUMN: Top 8 Most Popular Movies To Stream On Netflix Now', 'Netflix has always been one of the best platforms to stream movies. However, there are plenty of platforms available right now. Netflix is still one of the best among the others. It comes with a vast library and contains a lot of movies, TV series, and others. Whatever you need to watch, Netflix is the best destination.  \r\n\r\nIf you are new to the platform, you need to start with the most popular movies to stream on Netflix. Don’t worry, we are here to help you out and provide some best movies to stream on Netflix in this article. Make sure to go through the list of all these movies to find out all the details.', '<h2><strong>8 BEST POPULAR MOVIES TO STREAM ON NETFLIX&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">If you are reading this article, it means you want to find out the best movies to stream on Netflix. So, here is the list of best movies to stream on Netflix that you need to know. The story is briefly mentioned, which will help you choose.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-102\" class=\"ezoic-adpicker-ad\"></span><strong>1. &ldquo;THE BLIND SIDE&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">One of the most popular and good movies that you need to watch is &ldquo;The Blind Side.&rdquo; Sandra Bullock won an Oscar for her breathtaking performance in this movie. The movie is based on a true story where a teen without a home finds success on and off.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">The story of a traumatized boy on the road to becoming an all-American NFL and football player with the care of a woman and her family. The film is available on Netflix and you can watch anytime to have a very good movie watching experience.&nbsp;<span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-118\" class=\"ezoic-adpicker-ad\"></span></p>\r\n<h3><strong>2. &ldquo;SHERLOCK HOLMES: A GAME OF SHADOWS&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">If you think Robert Downey Jr. is only known for his performance in Avengers, you are very wrong. Apart from Avengers, the performance of RDJ in Sherlock Holmes is also known to be one of the best of all the movies of his life. It is one of the masterpieces you need to watch on Netflix. The comedy, action, story, and other aspects of the movie will help you to get a very good experience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>3. &ldquo;THE ADAM PROJECT&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">When it comes to choosing <a href=\"https://techtrendspro.com/best-free-movie-streaming-sites/\">free movie streaming sites to watch movies online</a>, the name of Netflix comes to mind. Most of the popular movies on Netflix are old, made around 2000.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">However, this one is one of the latest releases that features Ryan Reynolds, Zoe Saldana, Mark Ruffalo, and others. The movie is set about time traveling to the past and saving the future. You can add this film on your checklist as well.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>4. &ldquo;THE RENTAL&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">As the name suggests, the movie is about 2 couples taking a room together for a long weekend. There are many hidden cameras available in the house that could expose all the secrets to end the happy life of the couples.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">Also, someone is keeping tabs on them. The story is about how they survive and get out of the house. As the movie is based on a very realistic situation, it became very popular on Netflix.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>5. &ldquo;THE BUBBLE&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">Another movie that you need to watch on Netflix is &ldquo;The Bubble.&rdquo; The story of this movie is very different from all the other ones. It is based on a story where some actors are held together in a mansion to shoot a movie together. They are forced to shoot a comedy movie in the time of COVID. This movie is very different from all the other ones available on the list. Make sure to include it on your watching list.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>6. &ldquo;SHREK FOREVER AFTER&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">If you know the <a href=\"https://contentrally.com/ways-stream-free-movies-tv-shows-smartphone/\">ways to stream movies on your smartphone</a>, you know that Netflix provides the best features. However, when it comes to watching movies on this platform, you have to choose very carefully. &ldquo;Shrek Forever After&rdquo; is one of the movies that you need to watch on Netflix at least once in your life. It comes with a very good story and some other aspects of the life of the main character.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>7. &ldquo;FOUR BROTHERS&rdquo;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">You have downloaded the Netflix app, which is one of the <a href=\"https://www.smartbusinessdaily.com/best-apps-for-movies/\">best apps for movies</a>. If you do not know where to start, you can watch &ldquo;Four Brothers.&rdquo; It is a very good movie from 2005 that features Mark Wahlberg. Four brothers including adopted ones teams together to investigate the murder of their mother.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>8. &ldquo;BLOW&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"\">Last but not least, one of the movies of Johnny Deep also comes in this list is &ldquo;Blow.&rdquo; It is based on a true story and Johnny Deep delivered a very good performance. The story revolves around an American who became a very big cocaine smuggler. You can watch the movie on Netflix at high quality without any issues.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\"><strong><em>Read more:</em></strong> <a href=\"https://onlinehealthmedia.com/\">Online Health Media</a>&nbsp; &amp; <a href=\"https://techtrendspro.com/\">Tech Trends Pro</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.followthefashion.org/\">Follow The Fashion</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://wpbloggertips.com/\">Wp Blogger Tips</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.technetdeals.com/\">Tech Net Deals</a>.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>CONCLUSION&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">If you are new to Netflix, there are many things that you need to learn. However, the first thing that you need to figure out is what are the most popular movies that you need to watch. We are here to help you out with that and provide you with the list of best movies. Make sure to take a look at all the movies and choose the best one based on your choice.&nbsp;</p>', ' ', '1649800732-netflix.jpg', '1649800732-netflix1.jpg', 'guest-column-top-8-most-popular-movies-to-stream-on-netflix-now', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:28:52', 15),
(8, 21, '15, 14, 13', 'Best Survival Games On Steam', 'We all love survival games. Maybe there’s something hidden in our subconscious mind that needs to test our courage against the troubles in our ancient evolutionary past. Also, we like the excitement of depending on our senses to keep mutants or zombies out of our way.', '<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">1.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://greenhell-game.com/\">Green Hell</a></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Green Hell a undiscovered Amazon rainforest, in which you are left to defend yourself after being abandoned with nothing but a radio. Gameplay centers about caring for natural needs like building shelter, finding food, dangerous animals, and avoiding disease. A unique addition to this game is a Body Inspection Mode that enables you to manage your physical body by eliminating parasites, diagnosing yourself, and applying bandages. However, Green Hell is an equally psychological thriller since you will also need to control your psychological condition against an environment of isolation and other insanity-inducing environmental forces.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"Green Hell - Launch Trailer | PS4\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QF28UilEFcU?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">2.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://endnightgames.com/games/the-forest\">The Fores</a>t</span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The Forest welcomes you to a mysterious island populated by mutants that like to make you their next meal. The densely forested island and incorporates resources, both naturally occurring on the island and that you can retrieve from your crashed airplane. Survival involves managing the sources to build shelter and create weapons to battle with the mutants. Also, you have to ward off sickness and handle fire to stay warm and cook your food. Surviving is extra challenging because you will be hunted at night by the mutants, so solid shelter and traps are crucial to your survival.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"The Forest &ndash; PSX 2017: Multiplayer Trailer | PS4\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8KXfxHujIAA?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">3.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fallout.bethesda.net/en/games/fallout-4\">Fallout 4</a></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Fallout is a must-have for fans of the genre. You play as an unfortunate survivor of a catastrophic thermonuclear war. Alive only because you got cryogenically frozen in an undercovered nuclear fallout shelter. Unfortunately, your son got kidnapped, so you must wander out into the vast decaying wastelands in search of him, scavenging supplies and weaponry and fighting packs of enemies like Mole Rats and Raiders and Super Mutants. Fall Out 4&rsquo;s gameplay can be shifted between first-person and third-person like its predecessor</span><em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">,&nbsp;</span></em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Fallout 3. But, unlike Fallout 3, it adds a layered armor system and base-building.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"Fallout 4 - Launch Trailer\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/X5aJfebzkrM?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">4.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unknownworlds.com/subnautica/\">Subnautica</a></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Unknown Worlds Entertainment produced something completely original when it released this ocean-based, survival action-adventure in 2014. You play the character of a crew member of a spaceship that has fallen on an unfamiliar and remote planet, with one big problem there&rsquo;s no land in view, just the ocean. The survival method is quite addictive but also complicated. You endure your health, hunger, thirst, and oxygen levels by accumulating and harvesting items you find.<br /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"Subnautica Cinematic Trailer\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rz2SNm8VguE?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">5.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/p/ark\">Ark: Survival Evolved&nbsp;</a>&ndash; Survival Games</span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Ark: Survival Evolved has a unique variation to other survival games &ndash; dinosaurs. In this open-world survival, you wake in an expansive map packed full of ancient creatures so you need to craft and form a base to survive. You can play solo, with or opposite others since the game has both PvP and PvE modes. However, the dinosaurs are the thunderous appeal of this game. You will encounter more than 30, as well as a variety of different creatures. One of the best additions to</span><em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;</span></em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Ark: Survival Evolved is that once you have ample resources, you can feed and nourish the dinosaurs, then ride them to travel around the map or use them in battle.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"ARK II Announcement Trailer (1440p Final Version)\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RG2aOpCQQSA?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">6.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.klei.com/games/dont-starve\">Don&rsquo;t Starve</a></span></h3>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The name of this game speaks it all. The objective of Don&rsquo;t Starve is to craft, hunt, farm, and research things that are valuable so that you can eat and sustain in a different little world full of strange creatures and wonders. But, there are no directions, no hand-holding, and no help. It would benefit if you relied on your wit to make it through the game. Don&rsquo;t starve connects dark and comical visuals in a hand-drawn 2D art style that has helped create a solid following and overwhelmingly positive rating on Steam.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe title=\"Don\'t Starve Together 2021 Gameplay Trailer\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dU-aq2JbLkk?feature=oembed\" width=\"1170\" height=\"658\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Well done! You have come to the end of our list safe and unharmed. We hope you are now well equipped to overcome any hurdles that come your way.</span></p>', ' ', '1649800877-gamingg.jpg', '1649800877-gamingg1.jpg', 'best-survival-games-on-steam', '2022-04-13', 1, 1, NULL, '2022-04-13 03:31:17', 15);

